701
00:43:32,042 --> 00:43:34,476
Huh?

702
00:43:34,545 --> 00:43:37,139
Let's go.

703
00:43:38,182 --> 00:43:39,479
[phone rings]

704
00:43:39,550 --> 00:43:40,517
Ridley.

705
00:43:40,584 --> 00:43:41,915
