707
00:43:43,220 --> 00:43:44,949
Christ.

708
00:43:45,022 --> 00:43:45,989
You okay?

709
00:43:46,056 --> 00:43:47,353
Yeah, I'm fine.

710
00:43:47,424 --> 00:43:48,584
What about-

711
00:43:48,659 --> 00:43:50,092
Don't worry.

712
00:43:50,160 --> 00:43:51,684
