I find someone who can.

738
00:44:45,082 --> 00:44:47,346
If you'll excuse me
for saying so, Mr. Tolkin,

739
00:44:47,418 --> 00:44:48,510
you'll recall it was your man,

740
00:44:48,585 --> 00:44:50,985
